(1, 1, 'First Snow Fall', '["First Snowfall|Tuy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u00f9a","Today is November 26th.|H\\u00f4m nay l\\u00e0 26 th\\u00e1ng 11.","It snowed all day today.|Tuy\\u1ebft r\\u01a1i c\\u1ea3 ng\\u00e0y nay.","The snow is beautiful.|Tuy\\u1ebft th\\u1eadt \\u0111\\u1eb9p.","The snow finally stopped.|Tuy\\u1ebft cu\\u1ed1i c\\u00f9ng c\\u0169ng ng\\u1eebng r\\u01a1i.","My sister and I are excited.|Ch\\u1ecb(ho\\u1eb7c em g\\u00e1i) t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i r\\u1ea5t ph\\u1ea5n kh\\u00edch.","My Mom doesn''t like the snow.|M\\u1eb9 t\\u00f4i th\\u00ec ch\\u1eb3ng th\\u00edch tuy\\u1ebft.","My Mom has to shovel the drive way.|M\\u1eb9 ph\\u1ea3i d\\u1ecdn tuy\\u1ebft \\u1edf l\\u1ed1i ra v\\u00e0o.","My sister and I get to play.|Ch\\u1ecb t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i th\\u00ec \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u00f9a.","I put on my hat and mittens.|T\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ed9i m\\u0169 v\\u00e0 \\u0111eo g\\u0103ng tay v\\u00e0o.","My Mom puts on my scarf.|M\\u1eb9 t\\u00f4i cho\\u00e0ng kh\\u0103n c\\u1ed5 cho t\\u00f4i.","My Mom zippers my jacket.|M\\u1eb9 k\\u00e9o kh\\u00f3a \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c cho t\\u00f4i.","My sister puts on her hat and mittens.|Ch\\u1ecb t\\u00f4i \\u0111\\u1ed9i m\\u0169 v\\u00e0 \\u0111eo g\\u0103ng tay v\\u00e0o.","My Mom puts on her scarf.|M\\u1eb9 cho\\u00e0ng kh\\u0103n c\\u1ed5 cho ch\\u1ecb.","My Mom zippers her jacket.|M\\u1eb9 k\\u00e9o \\u00e1o kho\\u00e1c cho ch\\u1ecb.","My sister and I go outside.|Hai ch\\u1ecb em ra ngo\\u00e0i tr\\u1eddi.","We begin to make a snow man.|B\\u1ecdn t\\u00f4i b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u x\\u00e2y ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi tuy\\u1ebft.","My Mom starts to shovel the snow.|M\\u1eb9 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u d\\u1ecdn tuy\\u1ebft.","My sister and I make snow angels.|Ch\\u1ecb t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i n\\u1eb7n thi\\u00ean th\\u1ea7n tuy\\u1ebft.","My sister and I throw snowballs.|Hai \\u0111\\u1ee9a ch\\u01a1i n\\u00e9m tuy\\u1ebft.","It starts to snow again.|Tuy\\u1ebft l\\u1ea1i b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u r\\u01a1i n\\u1eefa.","We go inside for hot chocolate.|Ch\\u00fang t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0o trong nh\\u00e0 u\\u1ed1ng s\\u00f4c\\u00f4la n\\u00f3ng."]', 1),
(2, 1, 'Jessica''s First Day of School', '["Jessica''s First Day of School|Ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u \\u0111i h\\u1ecdc c\\u1ee7a Jessica.","Today is Jessica''s first day of kindergarten.|H\\u00f4m nay l\\u00e0 ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean \\u0111i h\\u1ecdc m\\u1eabu gi\\u00e1o c\\u1ee7a b\\u00e9 Jesssica.","Jessica and her parents walk to school.|Jessica v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 \\u0111i b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng.","Jessica''s Mom walks with her to her classroom.|M\\u1eb9 c\\u1ee7a Jessica \\u0111i c\\u00f9ng v\\u1edbi b\\u00e9 v\\u00e0o l\\u1edbp h\\u1ecdc.","Jessica meets her teacher.|Jessica g\\u1eb7p th\\u1ea7y m\\u00ecnh.","His name is Mr. Parker. |T\\u00ean th\\u1ea7y l\\u00e0 Parker.","The school bell rings at 8.45 A.M..|Chu\\u00f4ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng reo l\\u00ean l\\u00fac 8h45.","Jessica hugs and kisses her Mom goodbye.|Jessica \\u00f4m v\\u00e0 h\\u00f4n t\\u1ea1m bi\\u1ec7t m\\u1eb9.","Jessica''s Mom says ''I love you.''|M\\u1eb9 Jessica n\\u00f3i ''M\\u1eb9 y\\u00eau con''.","At 9.00 A.M., Jessica stands for the National anthem.|L\\u00fac 9h (s\\u00e1ng), Jessica \\u0111\\u1ee9ng d\\u1eady h\\u00e1t qu\\u1ed1c ca.","Mr. Parker calls out children''s names.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker g\\u1ecdi to t\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a c\\u00e1c b\\u00e9. (\\u0111i\\u1ec3m danh)","Each child yells back ''here!''|T\\u1eebng b\\u00e9 la l\\u1edbn l\\u00ean ''\\u0110\\u00e2y!''.","Mr. Parker teaches them about letters.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker d\\u1ea1y ch\\u00fang v\\u1ec1 c\\u00e1c ch\\u1eef c\\u00e1i.","Mr. Parker teaches them about numbers.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker d\\u1ea1y ch\\u00fang v\\u1ec1 c\\u00e1c con s\\u1ed1.","At 10:15 A.M. the students have recess.|L\\u00fac 10h15, h\\u1ecdc sinh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ra ch\\u01a1i.","Recess is fun.|Gi\\u1edd ch\\u01a1i r\\u1ea5t vui.","The students get to play and eat.|C\\u00e1c b\\u00e9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u01a1i v\\u00e0 \\u0103n.","At 10:30 A.M.|L\\u00fac 10h30.","the students go to gym class.|C\\u00e1c b\\u00e9 \\u0111\\u1ebfn ph\\u00f2ng t\\u1eadp th\\u1ec3 d\\u1ee5c.","At 11:15 A.M.|L\\u00fac 11h15.","the students return to Mr. Parker''s classroom.|C\\u00e1c b\\u00e9 tr\\u1edf v\\u1ec1 l\\u1edbp h\\u1ecdc c\\u1ee7a th\\u1ea7y Parker.","Mr. Parker tells the students to sit on the carpet.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker b\\u1ea3o c\\u00e1c h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00f2 ng\\u1ed3i xu\\u1ed1ng th\\u1ea3m.","Mr. Parker reads the students a story.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker \\u0111\\u1ecdc cho c\\u00e1c h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00f2 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e2u chuy\\u1ec7n.","Mr. Parker teaches the students a song.|Th\\u1ea7y Parker d\\u1ea1y cho c\\u00e1c h\\u1ecdc tr\\u00f2 m\\u1ed9t b\\u00e0i h\\u00e1t.","The lunch bell rings.|Chu\\u00f4ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng reo l\\u00ean.","Jessica''s first day of school is over.|Ng\\u00e0y \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ee7a Jessica \\u0111\\u00e3 k\\u1ebft th\\u00fac."]', 2),
(3, 1, 'My Flower Garden', '["My Flowers Garden|V\\u01b0\\u1eddn hoa c\\u1ee7a t\\u00f4i.","My name is Anne.|Con t\\u00ean l\\u00e0 Anne.","I love flowers.|Con r\\u1ea5t y\\u00eau hoa","I have a flower garden.|Con c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t v\\u01b0\\u1eddn hoa.","My garden is in front of my house.|Khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn \\u1edf tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc nh\\u00e0 c\\u1ee7a con.","My neighbour has a garden too.|H\\u00e0ng x\\u00f3m c\\u1ee7a con c\\u0169ng c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn.","My garden has different types of flowers.|V\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a con c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i hoa kh\\u00e1c nhau.","I have roses in my garden.|Con c\\u00f3 hoa h\\u1ed3ng trong v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","I have tulips in my garden.|Con c\\u00f3 hoa tulip trong v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","I have petunias in my garden.|Con c\\u00f3 hoa d\\u1ea1 y\\u00ean th\\u1ea3o trong v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","My garden has different colors.|Khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a con c\\u00f3 c\\u00e1c m\\u00e0u s\\u1eafc kh\\u00e1c nhau.","I plant red flowers.|Con tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i hoa m\\u00e0u \\u0111\\u1ecf.","I plant orange flowers.|Con tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i hoa m\\u00e0u cam.","I plant blue flowers.|Con tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i hoa m\\u00e0u xanh.","I plant purple flowers.|Con tr\\u1ed3ng c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i hoa m\\u00e0u t\\u00edm.","I take care of my garden.|Con ch\\u0103m s\\u00f3c khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","I water my garden every day.|Con t\\u01b0\\u1edbi n\\u01b0\\u1edbc cho v\\u01b0\\u1eddn h\\u1eb1ng ng\\u00e0y.","I kill the weeds in my garden.|Con di\\u1ec7t c\\u1ecf d\\u1ea1i trong v\\u01b0\\u1eddn.","I kill insects that eat my flowers.|Con di\\u1ec7t c\\u00e1c lo\\u1ea1i c\\u00f4n tr\\u00f9ng \\u0103n hoa.","I love my beautiful garden.|Con y\\u00eau khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh."]', 3),
(4, 1, 'Going Camping', '["Going Camping|\\u0110i c\\u1eafm tr\\u1ea1i","The Bright family went camping on the weekend.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111i c\\u1eafm tr\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o cu\\u1ed1i tu\\u1ea7n.","The Bright family went to Silent Lake.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1ebfn Silent Lake.","The Bright family left on Friday.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright r\\u1eddi \\u0111i v\\u00e0o th\\u1ee9 s\\u00e1u.","They camped for three days.|H\\u1ecd c\\u1eafm tr\\u1ea1i trong 3 ng\\u00e0y.","The Bright family brought a big tent.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright \\u0111em theo 1 c\\u00e1i l\\u1ec1u l\\u1edbn.","They brought a lot of food.|H\\u1ecd \\u0111em theo r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u \\u0111\\u1ed3 \\u0103n.","They brought insect repellent.|H\\u1ecd \\u0111em theo thu\\u1ed1c x\\u1ecbt c\\u00f4n tr\\u00f9ng.","The Bright family had a campfire on Friday.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright \\u0111\\u1ed1t l\\u1eeda tr\\u1ea1i v\\u00e0o th\\u1ee9 s\\u00e1u.","They roasted marshmallows.|H\\u1ecd n\\u01b0\\u1edbng k\\u1eb9o d\\u1ebbo.","They sang campfire songs.|H\\u1ecd h\\u00e1t c\\u00e1c b\\u00e0i h\\u00e1t l\\u1eeda tr\\u1ea1i.","On Saturday they went canoeing.|V\\u00e0o th\\u1ee9 7, h\\u1ecd \\u0111i b\\u01a1i xu\\u1ed3ng ca n\\u00f4.","On Saturday they went fishing.|V\\u00e0o th\\u1ee9 7, h\\u1ecdc \\u0111i c\\u00e2u c\\u00e1.","On Saturday they went swimming.|V\\u00e0o th\\u1ee9 7, h\\u1ecd \\u0111i b\\u01a1i.","They went hiking on Sunday.|H\\u1ecd \\u0111i leo n\\u00fai v\\u00e0o ch\\u1ee7 nh\\u1eadt.","The Bright family saw many birds.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright th\\u1ea5y nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i chim.","They saw blue jays.|H\\u1ecd th\\u1ea5y chim gi\\u1ebb c\\u00f9i xanh.","They saw hummingbirds.|H\\u1ecd th\\u1ea5y chim ru\\u1ed3i.","The Bright family saw many animals.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright th\\u1ea5y nhi\\u1ec1u lo\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u1ed9ng v\\u1eadt.","They saw a raccoon.|H\\u1ecd th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t con g\\u1ea5u m\\u00e8o.","They saw a squirrel.|H\\u1ecd th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t con s\\u00f3c.","But they didn''t see a bear.|Nh\\u01b0ng h\\u1ecd kh\\u00f4ng th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t con g\\u1ea5u n\\u00e0o.","The Bright family had a fun vacation.|Nh\\u00e0 Bright \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t k\\u00ec ngh\\u1ec9 th\\u00fa v\\u1ecb."]', 4),
(5, 1, 'My House', '["My House|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i","I live in a house.|T\\u00f4i s\\u1ed1ng trong m\\u1ed9t c\\u0103n nh\\u00e0.","My house is small.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i nh\\u1ecf.","My house has two bedrooms.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 2 ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1ee7.","My Mom and Dad sleep in one bedroom.|M\\u1eb9 v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed1 t\\u00f4i ng\\u1ee7 trong 1 ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1ee7.","My sister and I share the other bedroom.|Ch\\u1ecb t\\u00f4i v\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i chia s\\u1ebb c\\u00e1i ph\\u00f2ng ng\\u1ee7 c\\u00f2n l\\u1ea1i.","My house has a kitchen.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t nh\\u00e0 b\\u1ebfp.","My Mom and Dad cook dinner there every night.|M\\u1eb9 v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed1 t\\u00f4i n\\u1ea5u b\\u1eefa t\\u1ed1i \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00f3 m\\u1ed7i \\u0111\\u00eam.","My house has a living room.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u00f2ng kh\\u00e1ch.","My family watches television there every night.|Gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh t\\u00f4i xem tivi \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00f3 h\\u1eb1ng \\u0111\\u00eam.","My house has a big bathroom.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t ph\\u00f2ng t\\u1eafm l\\u1edbn.","My house has a lot of closets.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u t\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ef1ng \\u0111\\u1ed3.","My house has a basement.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t t\\u1ea7ng h\\u1ea7m.","My Dad has a workshop in the basement.|B\\u1ed1 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t x\\u01b0\\u1edfng l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c trong t\\u1ea7ng h\\u1ea7m.","My Dad makes wood furniture.|B\\u1ed1 t\\u00f4i l\\u00e0m \\u0111\\u1ed3 n\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea5t g\\u1ed7.","My house does not have a second floor.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 t\\u1ea7ng 2.","My house has a garage.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1i gara.","My house has a big backyard.|Nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn sau l\\u1edbn.","My backyard has a maple tree.|Khu v\\u01b0\\u1eddn sau nh\\u00e0 t\\u00f4i c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e2y phong.","My backyard has a