(8, 1, 'Mark''s Big Game', '["Mark''s Big Game|Tr\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ea5u l\\u1edbn c\\u1ee7a Mark.","Mark''s favorite sport is hockey.|M\\u00f4n th\\u1ec3 thao \\u01b0a th\\u00edch c\\u1ee7a Mark l\\u00e0 kh\\u00fac g\\u00f4n c\\u1ea7u.","He is 15 years old.|Ku nh\\u00f3c 15 tu\\u1ed5i.","Mark practises three times a week.|Mark luy\\u1ec7n t\\u1eadp 3 l\\u1ea7n m\\u1ed7i tu\\u1ea7n.","Practices are two hours long.|C\\u00e1c bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1eadp k\\u00e9o d\\u00e0i 2 ti\\u1ebfng.","Mark plays one game a week.|Mark ch\\u01a1i m\\u1ed9t tr\\u1eadn m\\u1ed7i tu\\u1ea7n.","Mark is a good hockey player.|Mark l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 hockey gi\\u1ecfi.","He plays on Friday nights.|C\\u1eadu ch\\u01a1i v\\u00e0o c\\u00e1c bu\\u1ed5i t\\u1ed1i th\\u1ee9 s\\u00e1u.","Friday night hockey games are popular.|C\\u00e1c tr\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ea5u t\\u1ed1i th\\u1ee9 s\\u00e1u r\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c \\u01b0a th\\u00edch.","Mark''s family watches him play.|Gia \\u0111\\u00ecnh Mark xem c\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u.","Mark''s friends watch him play too.|B\\u1ea1n b\\u00e8 Mark c\\u0169ng xem c\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u lu\\u00f4n.","There are always many fans.|Lu\\u00f4n c\\u00f3 r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u fans.","Tonight is the big game.|T\\u1ed1i nay l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t tr\\u1eadn quan tr\\u1ecdng.","Coaches are coming to watch Mark play.|C\\u00e1c hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n vi\\u00ean \\u0111\\u1ebfn xem Mark thi \\u0111\\u1ea5u.","Mark wants to play in the National Hockey League.|Mark mu\\u1ed1n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u01a1i \\u1edf gi\\u1ea3i hockey qu\\u1ed1c gia.","Mark wants to make a lot of money.|Mark mu\\u1ed1n ki\\u1ebfm th\\u1eadt nhi\\u1ec1u ti\\u1ec1n.","It is very hard to play in the NHL.|R\\u1ea5t kh\\u1ecf \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch\\u01a1i \\u1edf gi\\u1ea3i V\\u0110QG.","Mark''s parents want him to go to college.|B\\u1ed1 m\\u1eb9 Mark mu\\u1ed1n c\\u1eadu \\u0111i h\\u1ecdc \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u1ecdc.","They wa