(9, 1, 'The Easter Egg Hunt', '["The Easter Egg Hunt|S\\u0103n tr\\u1ee9ng Ph\\u1ee5c Sinh","Samantha is going to an Easter egg hunt.|Samantha s\\u1eafp \\u0111i s\\u0103n tr\\u1ee9ng Ph\\u1ee5c Sinh.","Tracey is going to an Easter egg hunt.|Tracey s\\u1eafp \\u0111i s\\u0103n tr\\u1ee9ng Ph\\u1ee5c Sinh.","The Easter egg hunt is at Sydney''s house.|Bu\\u1ed5i s\\u0103n tr\\u1ee9ng Ph\\u1ee5c Sinh \\u1edf nh\\u00e0 Sydney.","It is going to be fun.|S\\u1ebd r\\u1ea5t vui \\u0111\\u00e2y.","Sydney''s mom hid chocolate eggs.|M\\u1eb9 c\\u1ee7a Sydney gi\\u1ea5u m\\u1ea5y qu\\u1ea3 tr\\u1ee9ng (l\\u00e0m b\\u1eb1ng) socola.","Sydney''s mom hid chocolate bunnies.|M\\u1eb9 Sydney gi\\u1ea5u m\\u1ea5y con th\\u1ecf (th\\u1ecf con, rabbit = th\\u1ecf l\\u1edbn) socola.","Everybody is here.|M\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u1edf \\u0111\\u00e2y.","Everybody has an Easter basket.|M\\u1ed7i ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1i gi\\u1ecf Ph\\u1ee5c Sinh.","The Easter egg hunt can start.|Chuy\\u1ebfn s\\u0103n tr\\u1ee9ng ph\\u1ee5c sinh \\u0111\\u00e3 c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u.","Everybody must close their eyes.|M\\u1ecdi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ph\\u1ea3i nh\\u1eafm m\\u1eaft l\\u1ea1i.","One, two, three, go!|1, 2, 3, b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u.","Samantha finds an Easter egg.|Samantha t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t qu\\u1ea3 tr\\u1ee9ng ph\\u1ee5c sinh.","The Easter egg is behind a table.|Qu\\u1ea3 tr\\u1ee9ng \\u1edf \\u0111\\u1eb1ng sau m\\u1ed9t c\\u00e1i b\\u00e0n.","She puts it in her basket.|B\\u00e9 \\u1ea5y \\u0111\\u1eb7t n\\u00f3 v\\u00e0o trong gi\\u1ecf c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","Tracey finds a chocolate Easter bunny.|Tracey th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t con th\\u1ecf ph\\u1ee5c sinh.","It''s under the couch.|N\\u00f3 \\u1edf d\\u01b0\\u1edbi gh\\u1ebf sa l\\u00f4ng.","Tracey puts it in her basket.|Tracy \\u0111\\u1ec3 v\\u00e0o trong gi\\u1ecf c\\u1ee7a b\\u00e9.","Sydney finds a chocolate Easter bunny too.|Sydney c\\u0169ng th\\u1ea5y m\\u1