(10, 1, 'Joe''s First Car', '["Joe''s First Car|Chi\\u1ebfc xe h\\u01a1i \\u0111\\u1ea7u ti\\u00ean c\\u1ee7a Joe.","Joe is 18 years old.|Joe 18 tu\\u1ed5i.","Joe works at McDonald''s.|Joe l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c \\u1edf McDonald''s","Joe saves all his money.|Joe \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u00e0nh t\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 ti\\u1ec1n c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh.","Joe has 2500 dollars in the bank.|Joe c\\u00f3 2500 \\u0111\\u00f4 la trong ng\\u00e2n h\\u00e0ng.","He wants to buy a sports car.|C\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y mu\\u1ed1n mua m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc xe th\\u1ec3 thao.","Joe starts to look for a new car.|C\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc.","Joe looks in the newspaper.|Joe t\\u00ecm tr\\u00ean b\\u00e1o.","Joe looks in magazines.|Joe t\\u00ecm trong c\\u00e1c t\\u1ea1p ch\\u00ed.","Joe finds a car he likes.|Joe t\\u00ecm th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ed9t chi\\u1ebfc c\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y th\\u00edch.","Joe goes to see the car with his dad.|Joe \\u0111i xem chi\\u1ebfc xe v\\u1edbi b\\u1ed1 c\\u1ee7a c\\u1eadu.","He really likes it.|C\\u1eadu \\u1ea5y th\\u1ef1c s\\u1ef1 th\\u00edch n\\u00f3.","Joe doesn''t have enough money.|Joe kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ee7 ti\\u1ec1n.","Joe''s dad tells him to keep saving his money.|B\\u1ed1 Joe b\\u1ea3o c\\u1eadu h\\u00e3y ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u1ec3 d\\u00e0nh ti\\u1ec1n.","Joe wants this car a lot.|Joe mu\\u1ed1n chi\\u1ebfc xe qu\\u00e1 x\\u00e1.","Joe asks his dad to help him.|Joe nh\\u1edd b\\u1ed1 gi\\u00fap m\\u00ecnh.","Joe and his dad make a deal.|Joe v\\u00e0 b\\u1ed1 th\\u1ecfa thu\\u1eadn v\\u1edbi nhau.","Joe''s dad will lend him the money.|B\\u1ed1 Joe s\\u1ebd cho c\\u1eadu m\\u01b0\\u1ee3n ti\\u1ec1n.","Joe must work hard.|Joe ph\\u1ea3i l\\u00e0m vi\\u1ec7c ch\\u0103m ch\\u1ec9.","He must pay the money back to his dad.|C\\u1eadu ph\\u1ea3i tr\\u1ea3 l\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ec1n cho b\\u1ed1.","Joe is very happy.|Joe r\\u1ea5t vui.","Joe owns his first car.|Jow s\\u1edf h\\u1eefu chi\\u1ebfc xe \\u0